-- Japan Post agrees to take 40 pct stake in Saison Asset Management
-- By Junko Fujita
-- Fri Sep 26, 2014 03:51AM EDT
-- None



TOKYO, Sept 26 (Reuters) - Japan Post Co said on Friday it has agreed to take a 40 percent stake in Saison Asset Management Co, an asset management unit of Credit Saison Co Ltd <8253.T>, a credit card company with about 35 million users.

Japan Post sells postal, savings and insurance services through its 24,000 post offices nationwide.